'''耶孙墓'''是一个[[马加比家族|马加比时期]]的古墓，在[[以色列|以色列]][[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]的Rehavia社区发现。它已被确定为耶孙的墓地，可能是一位海军军官，因为在墓穴里发现两艘军舰的图画。 
[[File:Jason's_Tomb_Inscription.JPG|thumb]]
铭文表明，耶孙曾航行到埃及的海岸。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jewishmag.com/47mag/jerusalemtombs/jerusalemtombs.htm |title=Jerusalem tombs |accessdate=2016-03-02 |archive-date=2018-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309163240/http://www.jewishmag.com/47mag/jerusalemtombs/jerusalemtombs.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

耶孙墓用一根[[多立克柱式|多立克柱]]装饰墓室入口，上面是金字塔形屋顶。纪念死者的铭文使用希腊文和阿拉姆文<ref>[http://www.mfa.gov.il/MFA/History/Early%20History%20-%20Archaeology/Archaeological%20Sites%20in%20Israel%20-%20Jerusalem-%20Burial Archaeological Sites in Israel - Jerusalem: Burial Sites and Tombs of the Second Temple Period<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731154454/http://www.mfa.gov.il/MFA/History/Early%20History%20-%20Archaeology/Archaeological%20Sites%20in%20Israel%20-%20Jerusalem-%20Burial |date=2016-07-31 }}</ref>。

